# Web Business Dashboard (React + TanStack Router)

## Tech Stack
- **React 19** + **TypeScript 5.8** with Vite 7.0
- **TanStack Router** for type-safe file-based routing
- **Zustand** for client state management
- **Tailwind CSS 4.x** + **shadcn/ui** for styling
- **React Hook Form** + **Zod** for form validation
- **FullCalendar** for class scheduling

## Key Features
- **Business dashboard** with analytics and onboarding
- **Calendar management** with drag-drop scheduling
- **Venue management** with image uploads
- **Class template system** with instance generation
- **Earnings dashboard** with CSV export
- **Settings management** with tabbed interface

## Component Architecture
- **Feature-based organization** - components grouped by business domain
- **shadcn/ui patterns** - consistent styling and behavior
- **Composition over inheritance** - flexible, reusable components
- **Accessibility** - built on Radix UI primitives

## Form Management
- **React Hook Form + Zod** pattern for all forms
- **No explicit generic types** - let TypeScript infer from Zod schemas
- **Field validation** with proper error attribution
- **Loading states** and optimistic updates

## Calendar Integration
- **FullCalendar** with drag-drop, resize, and real-time updates
- **Business timezone** - all times in business local timezone
- **Event transformations** - convert backend data to calendar format
- **Real-time sync** - updates immediately when backend changes

## State Management
- **Server state**: Convex subscriptions for real-time backend data
- **Client state**: Zustand for authentication and app-level state
- **URL state**: nuqs for settings tabs, filters, and shareable state

## Styling
- **Tailwind CSS 4.x** with latest features
- **shadcn/ui** components with theme system
- **Light/dark mode** support
- **Mobile responsive** - desktop-first with mobile breakpoints